metadata.name: The Spider and The Flower
metadata.description:
Life Around Us is a series of one of one photographs taken on our journey as our family circum navigates the globe on a sailboat.

The Spider and The Flower is the first release in the series. Inspired by our home today, taken in early spring as life begins to emerge from the snow. It signifies the beginning of our journey and the life we're leaving behind.

Journey with us around the world as we sail across oceans, sharing all the sights, animals, and people the world has to offer.
